<text top="1063" left="342" width="486" height="11" font="4"><i>Council. </i>Corrections should be submitted to original speeches only. They should be incorporated</text>
<text top="1077" left="342" width="486" height="11" font="2">in a copy of the record and be sent under the signature of a member of the delegation concerned,</text>
<text top="1092" left="342" width="486" height="11" font="4"><i>within one week of the date of publication</i>, to the Chief of the Verbatim Reporting Service,</text>
